    "body": "Until your request works, as a workaround I believe you can accomplish an \"only you\" sound notification with code like: \n\n``` lua\n-- 'p' is a player object, maybe it's the new owner\n-- Use 'IsLocalPlayer', which will only be 'true' for the game belonging to the new owner\nif p.IsLocalPlayer then\n    Media.PlaySound(\"ONLYYOU.AUD\")\nend\n```\n"
